Source: landscape-client
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Landscape Team <landscape-team@canonical.com>
AUTOPPA_INCLUDE(dapper,feisty,gutsy,hardy):Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5)
AUTOPPA_INCLUDE(intrepid):Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 6.0.7~), po-debconf
