Description: The Landscape administration system client
 Landscape is a web-based tool for managing Ubuntu systems. This
 package is necessary if you want your machine to be managed in a
 Landscape account.
 .
 This package provides the core libraries.

Package: landscape-client
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: python
AUTOPPA_INCLUDE(dapper):Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libcurl3 (>= 7.15.1-1ubuntu3), python-twisted-web, python2.4-pycurl, hal, smartpm-core (>= 1.1), cron
AUTOPPA_INCLUDE(feisty,gutsy,hardy):Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python-twisted-web, python-pycurl, hal, smartpm-core (>= 1.1), cron
AUTOPPA_INCLUDE(intrepid):Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, landscape-common, hal, python-twisted-web, python-smartpm, python-pycurl, cron
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Description: The Landscape administration system client
 Landscape is a web-based tool for managing Ubuntu systems. This
 package is necessary if you want your machine to be managed in a
 Landscape account.
 .
 This package provides the Landscape client and requires a Landscape account.
